Package: proDD
Type: Package
Title: Differentially detection of proteins in label-free mass spectrometry data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Constantin", "Ahlmann-Eltze", email = "artjom31415@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Simon", "Anders", email="s.anders@zmbh.uni-heidelberg.de", role="ths"))
Description: The package implements a Bayesian model to handle label-free
    mass spectrometry data. The model takes into account the missing observations
    which occur at low intensity using a probabilistic dropout model. It can
    be used to infer which proteins differ between conditons and provides
    additional methods to estimate the dropout probability curves, the sample
    distances and other useful functions.
